Good morning,

Today=E2=80=99s Daily Update interview is another installment of the Strate=
chery Founder series; as a reminder, one of the challenges in covering star=
tups is the lack of available data. My solution is to go in the opposite di=
rection and interview founders directly, letting them give their subjective=
 overview of their companies, while pressing them on their business model, =
background, and long-term potential.

Today=E2=80=99s interview is with Deel Co-Founder and CEO Alex Bouaziz ( ht=
tps://twitter.com/Bouazizalex ). Deel is a human resources platform with a =
